{
    "id": "chapter2_forest_whispers",
    "title": "第二章：林中密语",
    "description": "晨曦营地东边的低语森林最近传出异样的声响——树木在低语，迷雾中隐约有身影移动。阿卡娅希望你调查这片森林深处，寻找异常的源头。",
    "start_node": "start",
    "requires_completed": ["chapter1_wake_up"],
    "nodes": {
        "start": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "晨曦的阳光洒在营地上，你整理好装备走出小屋。\n西边哨站的任务已经完成，但你心中总有一个声音在提醒你——这个世界远比想象中广阔。",
            "next": "akaya_call"
        },
        "akaya_call": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「你来得正好！我正想找你。」\n阿卡娅从营地东边的瞭望台上快步走下来，神色比平时严肃了几分。",
            "next": "forest_setup"
        },
        "forest_setup": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「营地向东大约走两天的路程，有一片叫『低语森林』的地方。\n本来那里很安静，但最近......」\n她顿了顿，似乎在斟酌用词。",
            "next": "forest_problem"
        },
        "forest_problem": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「巡逻队报告说，那片森林在『说话』。不是风声，不是动物声——是真正的低语声。\n而且，进去调查的三个人，只有一个回来了。」",
            "next": "forest_reaction_choice"
        },
        "forest_reaction_choice": {
            "type": "CHOICE",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "她直视着你的眼睛：\n「我需要一个靠得住的人。你愿意去一趟吗？」",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "「当然，我去看看。」",
                    "next": "accept_mission",
                    "flags": {"accepted_ch2_quest": true, "ch2_brave": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "「低语？会不会是听错了？」",
                    "next": "skeptical_approach",
                    "flags": {"ch2_skeptical": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "「回来的那个人说了什么？」",
                    "next": "ask_details",
                    "flags": {"ch2_inquisitive": true}
                }
            ]
        },
        "skeptical_approach": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「我也希望是听错了。但那个回来的人——他一直在重复同一句话。」\n她的声音低了下去：「『树在叫我的名字。』」",
            "next": "accept_mission"
        },
        "ask_details": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「他......不太好。一直缩在角落，嘴里念叨着什么『树根下面有东西』。\n医疗队说他受了强烈的精神冲击，可能需要好几周才能恢复。」\n她摇了摇头，神情凝重。",
            "next": "accept_mission"
        },
        "accept_mission": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「好，我就知道你靠得住。」\n她从腰间解下一枚泛着微光的吊坠，递到你手中。",
            "next": "give_talisman"
        },
        "give_talisman": {
            "type": "EVENT",
            "text": "阿卡娅递给你一枚温暖的木质吊坠。",
            "event": {
                "type": "give_item",
                "value": "minecraft:golden_apple",
                "params": {
                    "count": 1
                }
            },
            "next": "talisman_explain"
        },
        "talisman_explain": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「这是用晨曦营地边上的古树心材做的护身符，带着它，能抵御一些......不干净的东西。」\n她笑了笑，但笑容里有一丝忧虑。",
            "next": "quest_start_node"
        },
        "quest_start_node": {
            "type": "QUEST_START",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「你的任务是：找到森林异变的源头。可能需要先穿过低语森林外围，到达中心区域。\n注意那些被腐化的生物——它们已经不是普通的动物了。」",
            "quest": {
                "quest_id": "investigate_whispering_forest",
                "quest_name": "§5调查低语森林",
                "quest_description": "前往晨曦营地以东的低语森林，调查异象的源头。到达森林中心区域并清除腐化之源。",
                "objectives": [
                    {
                        "type": "REACH_LOCATION",
                        "targetId": "forest_edge",
                        "count": 1,
                        "displayText": "到达低语森林边缘"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "KILL_MOB",
                        "targetId": "minecraft:zombie",
                        "count": 8,
                        "displayText": "击杀被腐化的生物 × 8"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "REACH_LOCATION",
                        "targetId": "forest_heart",
                        "count": 1,
                        "displayText": "到达森林中心"
                    }
                ],
                "rewards": {
                    "exp": 120,
                    "items": ["minecraft:iron_sword:1", "minecraft:enchanted_golden_apple:1"],
                    "flags": {"completed_ch2_investigation": "true"}
                },
                "on_quest_complete": "quest_complete_dialog",
                "on_quest_fail": "quest_fail_dialog"
            },
            "next": "forest_warning"
        },
        "forest_warning": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「还有一件事——如果进入森林深处后听到了有人叫你的名字，不要回头，不要应答。\n直接往前走。」\n她的语气不容置疑。",
            "next": "stranger_encounter_cond"
        },
        "stranger_encounter_cond": {
            "type": "CONDITION",
            "condition": {
                "type": "FLAG_CHECK",
                "targetId": "ch2_skeptical",
                "value": 1,
                "operator": "==",
                "nextIfTrue": "akaya_challenge",
                "nextIfFalse": "departure"
            }
        },
        "akaya_challenge": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "阿卡娅",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar11.png",
            "text": "「我知道你在想什么——『这怎么可能』。」\n她微微一笑，但眼神很认真。\n「我曾经也不信。直到我亲眼看到那片森林吞噬了一个人的影子。」",
            "next": "departure"
        },
        "departure": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你整理好行装，告别了阿卡娅，踏上了前往东方的路。\n风中隐隐约约传来什么声音——是树木在窃窃私语吗？\n还是你的心跳声？",
            "next": "forest_edge_arrival"
        },
        "forest_edge_arrival": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "两天的路程在你的脚下缩短。\n当你看到前方那片灰雾笼罩的林地时，你知道——你到了。\n\n低语森林的入口处立着一块古老的石碑，上面刻着模糊的文字。",
            "next": "examine_stone"
        },
        "examine_stone": {
            "type": "CHOICE",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "text": "石碑上刻着文字，但大部分已经被风化和苔藓覆盖。\n你隐约认出几个字：",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "仔细辨认碑文",
                    "next": "read_stone_1",
                    "flags": {"ch2_read_stone": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "直接进入森林",
                    "next": "enter_forest_direct",
                    "flags": {"ch2_enter_direct": true}
                }
            ]
        },
        "read_stone_1": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你拨开苔藓，勉强读出了碑文的内容：\n\n「于低语之地，心诚则明。\n迷失者入，坚定者出。\n万籁俱寂之时，真相自现。」\n\n底部似乎还有一个标记——那是一棵古老的橡树图案。",
            "next": "enter_forest_cont"
        },
        "enter_forest_direct": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你没有在石碑前多做停留，径直踏入了森林。\n雾气在你脚下翻滚，树木的枝叶在头顶交叉成一张密不透风的网。\n身后的光线越来越远。",
            "next": "forest_mist"
        },
        "enter_forest_cont": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你将碑文记在心中，深吸一口气，跨过了森林的边界。\n就在你踏入的瞬间，周围的声音仿佛被什么东西抽走了——\n世界安静得可怕。",
            "next": "forest_mist"
        },
        "forest_mist": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "???",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「喂——那边的！」\n一个急促的声音从侧面传来。\n你猛地转身，看到雾气中有一个身影——那人手中握着一张弓，箭头正对着你身后的方向。",
            "next": "stranger_intro"
        },
        "stranger_intro": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "???",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「别动——」\n一声弦响，一支箭从你耳边呼啸而过。\n你身后传来什么重物倒地的闷响。你转过身，看到一只浑身缠绕着黑色雾气的野狼倒在几米外。",
            "next": "stranger_meet"
        },
        "stranger_meet": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「呼——好险。你没事吧？」\n那人收起弓，从雾气中走出来。\n那是一个年轻的猎手，穿着深绿色的斗篷，腰间挂着一串写满符文的木牌。",
            "next": "stranger_talk"
        },
        "stranger_talk": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「我是菲恩，在这片森林附近住了大半辈子。\n这几天林子里的情况越来越不对劲了——腐化生物的数量翻了十倍不止。」\n他皱着眉，看向森林深处。",
            "next": "fen_intro_choice"
        },
        "fen_intro_choice": {
            "type": "CHOICE",
            "speaker": "你",
            "text": "你要怎么回应菲恩？",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "「我是从晨曦营地来的，来调查森林异变。」",
                    "next": "ally_path",
                    "flags": {"ch2_ally_fen": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "「你一直住在这里？知道森林中间有什么吗？」",
                    "next": "info_path",
                    "flags": {"ch2_ask_fen": true}
                }
            ]
        },
        "ally_path": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「晨曦营地？你们总算派人来了。」\n他的表情明显放松了一些。\n「太好了，我正愁一个人搞不定呢。这片森林需要一个向导——如果你愿意，我可以带你走安全的路线。」",
            "next": "fen_join"
        },
        "info_path": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「森林中间......」\n他的表情阴郁下来。\n「如果我的推测没错，那里有一棵被腐化的古树——所有的低语都是从那里传出来的。我试着接近过两次，都被逼退了回来。」",
            "next": "fen_join"
        },
        "fen_join": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「不管你是为了什么来的——一个人走这片森林都不安全。我正好要去找腐化的源头，一起走吧？」\n他伸出手，露出手腕上的一串编绳。\n「放心，我熟悉这里的每一寸土地。」",
            "next": "journey_deeper"
        },
        "journey_deeper": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你和菲恩一同深入森林。\n周围的树木越来越扭曲，雾气中偶尔闪过可疑的影子。\n远处传来若有若无的低语声——像是很多人同时在说话，又像是风声穿过树洞。",
            "next": "whispers_start"
        },
        "whispers_start": {
            "type": "CHOICE",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "text": "低语声越来越清晰了。你似乎听到了自己的名字！\n菲恩的呼吸急促起来，他握紧了弓。",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "「你听到了吗？」",
                    "next": "fen_response_1",
                    "flags": {"ch2_confirm_whispers": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "无视低语，继续前进",
                    "next": "push_forward",
                    "flags": {"ch2_ignore_whispers": true}
                }
            ]
        },
        "fen_response_1": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「嗯。它们在叫我的名字——用我母亲的声音。」\n他的声音有些发颤，但脚步没有停下。\n「别理它们。阿卡娅说得对——不要回应，不要回头。」",
            "next": "push_forward"
        },
        "push_forward": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你和菲恩并肩前行，脚下的路越来越狭窄。\n周围的树木上开始出现一种黑色的苔藓，散发着淡淡的腐臭味。\n低语声越来越大——但你始终没有回头。",
            "next": "arrival_heart"
        },
        "arrival_heart": {
            "type": "EVENT",
            "text": "森林中央出现了一片空地。",
            "event": {
                "type": "play_sound",
                "value": "minecraft:entity.warden.heartbeat",
                "params": {
                    "volume": 1.0
                }
            },
            "next": "corrupted_tree"
        },
        "corrupted_tree": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "森林中央是一棵巨大的橡树——或者说，曾经是。\n黑色的藤蔓缠绕着树干，树冠上倒挂着某种暗紫色的结晶体，\n像心脏一样在有节奏地跳动着。每一次跳动，都有一圈暗色的涟漪向四周扩散。",
            "next": "fen_awed"
        },
        "fen_awed": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「这就是了......」\n他的声音几乎是耳语。「腐化的源头。那些低语——都是从这棵树的树根下发出的。\n我能感觉到......有什么东西在下面。」",
            "next": "final_choice"
        },
        "final_choice": {
            "type": "CHOICE",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "他看向你：\n「你来做决定。我们要怎么做？」",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "「烧了它——斩草除根。」",
                    "next": "burn_choice",
                    "flags": {"ch2_burn_tree": true}
                },
                {
                    "label": "「先调查树根下面有什么。」",
                    "next": "investigate_roots",
                    "flags": {"ch2_examine_roots": true}
                }
            ]
        },
        "burn_choice": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「好——直接解决问题。」\n他从背包里取出一个油壶和打火石。\n「这片森林需要一场净化。你来点火，我在后面掩护你。」",
            "next": "climax_battle"
        },
        "investigate_roots": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「也好，先弄清楚我们面对的是什么。」\n他蹲下身，拨开树根旁的泥土。\n「帮我盯着周围——我觉得这东西不会让我们轻易窥探它的秘密。」",
            "next": "climax_battle"
        },
        "climax_battle": {
            "type": "EVENT",
            "text": "就在你们行动的瞬间，树根猛地从地面炸开！",
            "event": {
                "type": "command",
                "value": "summon minecraft:zombie ~ ~ ~ {PersistenceRequired:1b, CustomName:'\"腐化守卫\"', Attributes:[{Name:\"generic.max_health\",Base:40}]}",
                "params": {}
            },
            "next": "fen_fight"
        },
        "fen_fight": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
            "portrait": "shade:textures/gui/portrait/avatar5.png",
            "text": "「小心——！」\n菲恩拉开弓，一箭射向破土而出的腐化怪物。\n「我来拖住它！你快去——不管是要烧还是挖——快动手！」",
            "next": "quest_target_update"
        },
        "quest_target_update": {
            "type": "QUEST_UPDATE",
            "text": "目标更新：击败腐化守卫，净化古树之根！",
            "next": "battle_aftermath_cond"
        },
        "battle_aftermath_cond": {
            "type": "CONDITION",
            "condition": {
                "type": "FLAG_CHECK",
                "targetId": "ch2_burn_tree",
                "value": 1,
                "operator": "==",
                "nextIfTrue": "purify_fire",
                "nextIfFalse": "purify_light"
            }
        },
        "purify_fire": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "火焰沿着黑色的藤蔓蔓延，发出刺耳的嘶鸣声。\n那些暗紫色的结晶体在高温中炸裂开来，化为黑色的烟尘消散在空中。\n古树发出了一声低沉的呻吟——仿佛是终于解脱了的叹息。\n低语声停止了。森林安静了下来。",
            "next": "victory"
        },
        "purify_light": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "叙述",
            "portrait": "",
            "text": "你拨开泥土和藤蔓，在树根下发现了一枚散发着微弱光芒的种子。\n当你触碰到它的瞬间，一股温暖的力量从指尖涌遍全身。\n黑色的腐化物质像被阳光照射的雾气一样消散了。\n古树的叶片重新泛起了绿色。低语声化为了一声温柔的叹息。",
            "next": "victory"
        },
        "victory": {
            "type": "DIALOG",
            "speaker": "菲恩",
